anySearch API - Message Handling & Admin Panel
🚀 Developed by Mohd Shuaib (Codermshuaibsi)

This API powers the message handling system for anySearch, allowing users to submit and retrieve messages. Additionally, it includes an admin panel accessible from the root (/) route, which serves an index.html page for managing messages.

🔗 API Endpoints
1️⃣ Admin Panel
📌 Route: /
📝 Description: Serves an index.html page for the admin panel.

Navigating to / opens the admin panel (index.html), where administrators can view  messages.

This is a static page that provides an easy-to-use interface for monitoring user messages.

2️⃣ Fetch All Messages
📌 Endpoint: GET /api/allmessages
📌 Description: Retrieves all stored messages from MongoDB.
📌 Response: Returns a JSON array of message objects.
