📌 Validation Rules:
✔ All fields (name, email, message) are required.
✔ The message must be at least 5 characters long.

🛠️ Technologies Used
Node.js (Server-side runtime)

Express.js (Web framework)

MongoDB + Mongoose (Database and ODM)

CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)

Static File Serving (index.html for admin panel)

⚡ How It Works
Users submit messages → Data is validated and stored in MongoDB.

Admin panel (/) → Admins can access index.html to view and manage messages.

Retrieve messages → Use /api/allmessages to fetch all stored messages.

This API makes managing user inquiries & feedback seamless while providing a dedicated admin panel for monitoring submissions. 🚀